name: Manhattan
comments: a songbook full of classics by the one and only a voice for the ages lady ella
I love the songs that she sang. She had a very beautiful voice when she sang. I love the songs and to listen to them from such a long time ago.
ah, the sweet sounds of yester year
Gorgeous classic. I see it like it was yesterday.
I personally enjoyed Ella's singing - even standards - to her scat singing, although that was pretty good too.
as with most music she approaches...ella owns manhattan...

Animatu berriro ondoren, bere dirua zenbatzen zuen, eta dyeable bere ile ilehoria. Laburbilduz: bit eskizofrenikoa da.
Simply wonderful...put's me in a positive mood instantly. My favorite singer!
